Class DataverseResponse<D>

  • java.lang.Object
    • nl.knaw.dans.lib.dataverse.DataverseResponse<D>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    DataverseHttpResponse

    public class DataverseResponse<D>
extends Object

    Response from Dataverse. A typical response from Dataverse is a JSON document with the following format:

     {
   "status": "OK",
   "data": {
       "myfield": "myvalue"
   }
 }
